title: Stephen Hales (died 1574)
text:
Stephen Hales (died 1574) was an English politician.
He was a <a href="Member%20of%20Parliament">Member</a> (MP) of the <a href="Parliament%20of%20England">Parliament of England</a> for <a href="Great%20Bedwyn%20%28UK%20Parliament%20constituency%29">Great Bedwyn</a> in 1563 and <a href="Leicester%20%28UK%20Parliament%20constituency%29">Leicester</a> in 1571.
